{"tid":1001643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啟德跑道商業地流標","createTime":"2019-01-30T09:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T10:28:13.000Z","uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0aafbc7c74fc7b640b8ff236d3e53e53a5488264","tid":1001643,"uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:57:56.000Z","msg":"啟德跑道商業地流標<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-content/NOW.921164/latest-news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-content%2FNOW.921164%2Flatest-news&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=db6346b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-content/NOW.921164/latest-news</a><br />\n<br />\n地政總署公布，九龍啟德第4C區5號商業/酒店地因地價標金未達到政府所定的底價而流標。<br />\n<br />\n上述用地為啟德跑道區首幅商業用地，最高可建樓面面積約61.2萬平方呎，指定作非工業用途(不包括住宅、倉庫及加油站但包括酒店)，市場估值介乎89億元至98億元。地皮上周五(1月25日)截標，共接獲9份標書，包括長實(<a href=\"http://01113.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01113.HK&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=5d1082bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01113.HK</a>)  +0.100 (+0.153%)    沽空 $1.04億; 比率 21.690%   、信置(<a href=\"http://00083.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00083.HK&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=4049a6d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00083.HK</a>)  -0.180 (-1.278%)    沽空 $6.50百萬; 比率 5.196%   、嘉華(<a href=\"http://00173.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00173.HK&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=a2b1966a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00173.HK</a>)  +0.080 (+1.909%)    沽空 $1.07百萬; 比率 6.732%   、鷹君(<a href=\"http://00041.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00041.HK&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=f3e41705\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00041.HK</a>)  +0.300 (+0.833%)    沽空 $10.83萬; 比率 1.860%   、Astute Max、建灝地產、遠展(<a href=\"http://00035.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00035.HK&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=2cdcf6f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00035.HK</a>)  +0.010 (+0.287%)    沽空 $2.79萬; 比率 1.630%   、九龍倉置業(<a href=\"http://01997.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01997.HK&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=6c58b7f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01997.HK</a>)  +0.250 (+0.479%)    沽空 $2.40千萬; 比率 18.463%   及新地(<a href=\"http://00016.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00016.HK&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=6b389263\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00016.HK</a>)  +1.100 (+0.848%)    沽空 $1.82億; 比率 22.231%   ，由於沒有任何標價達到政府專業估價師所評估的底價，政府不接納上述九份標書。(ac/a)(報價延遲最少十五分鐘。沽空資料截至 2019-01-30 16:25。)"},{"pid":"fe10c470159828ea80484103e9e681f74fe2a5aa","tid":1001643,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:05:46.000Z","msg":"事實證明<br />\n根本政府先抬高地價嘅最大元兇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70fbe3ffa96e7f9c1986b1cc074bdfdd2fc6a8a6","tid":1001643,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe10c470159828ea80484103e9e681f74fe2a5aa","tid":1001643,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:05:46.000Z","msg":"事實證明<br />\n根本政府先抬高地價嘅最大元兇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:28:13.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥：樓價太高了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥：想地價平啲？你諗都唔使諗呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}